<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,223,1295]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,1231,1257]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name of the new genus refers to the boreal climate zone, where the 
<typeStatus box="[1185,1236,1232,1258]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">type</typeStatus>
species has been collected. Gender masculine.
</paragraph>
